292
00:27:02,079 --> 00:27:03,264
Hi, honey.

293
00:27:07,774 --> 00:27:09,041
Oh, the ice cream.

294
00:27:11,405 --> 00:27:12,556
Honey,

295
00:27:13,204 --> 00:27:14,618
you know how it is.

