00:28:52,327 --> 00:28:54,920
Karen, maybe Jerry isn't the guy...

308
00:28:55,299 --> 00:28:58,303
but you don't know him like I do,
or see him down in the basement.

309
00:28:59,178 --> 00:29:02,230
